Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:54.85,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也依然想要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:23:00.61,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你一定也经历过
